OL,5,G2200 Bangers & Cash: Restoring Classics
OL,6,     FA35/BMW Z3: The team take on one
OL,7,     Fof Derek's favourites - an Austin
OL,8,     FA35 - but its age ensures some
OL,9,     Fhefty bills. To bank some cash,
OL,10,     Ftheir second project is a quick
OL,11,     Fflip - a 1999 BMW Z3.
